high_descs: turn right and walk forwards, then hang a right and walk until you reach the front of the kitchen table
grab a spoon off of the kitchen table
turn around and walk forwards to the fridge
place the spoon on a plate in the fridge
grab the plate out of the fridge
turn left and walk forwards to the kitchen counter, then turn left and walk down to the far end of the counters
place the plate inside of the sink
anns.task_desc: place a plate with a spoon on it inside of the sink

high_descs: Turn right, move towards the silver trash can, then turn right and move to the center of the wooden table and turn right to face the table.
Pick up the ladle with the black handle in the middle of the table between the fork and the toaster.
Turn around and move to the gray refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator doors and place the ladle on top of the gray plate on the middle shelf.
Pick up the plate with the ladle on top from the middle refrigerator shelf and close both refrigerator doors.
Turn to the left, move to the range, then turn to the left and move to the sink and turn right to face the counter.
Place the gray plate with the ladle on top in the sink between the apple and the green sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a ladle into the sink.

high_descs: Move to the left side of the kitchen table across from the fridge
Pick up ladle from the table
Move to the fridge behind you to the right of the sink
Open the fridge, place the ladle on the plate
Pick up the plate and close the door to the fridge
Move to the kitchen sink the left of the fridge and to the right of the table
Place the plate in the kitchen sink
anns.task_desc: Put the plate from the fridge with the ladle on it in the sink.
